title: Battle Factory [Action, Eng, 2018]
description:
Information was received that a car full of gold was hidden at one of the abandoned factories. So you were sent to the factory, but of course you were not alone there. Your department tried to keep it a secret, but word got out and the place is teaming with mercenaries. Find the treasure before they do.
The factory is full of weapons.
 
Control keys:

WASD - Character Movement
SPACEBAR - Jump
SHIFT - Sprint
1,2,3,4,5 ...- Weapon change
R - Reload
Esc - Exit the menu
LMB - Shoot
RMB - Aim

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 2 GHz
RAM: 512 mb
VRAM: 256 mb
HDD: 606 mb
